#ident "%W% %E%"
#
#	File name: engage.ipahostgrpstress
#
#	This file contains the operations specific to the ipahostgrpstress tests.
#	It is targetted to be included by the main script "run" and not be be 
#	used alone.
#
#	Replace the "xyz" by your name (e.g. "schema") and "Xyz" by your
#	name (e.g. "Schema").
#
#
#	History
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# dd/mm/yy | Author  	  | Comments
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 05/22/09 | JGalipea     | Creation
